<p xmlns="http://docs.oasis-open.org/legaldocml/ns/akn/3.0">(Official Journal of the European Union L 348 of 29 December 2017)</p>On page 3, point (7)(b) of Article 1, new Article 47c(1):<p xmlns="http://docs.oasis-open.org/legaldocml/ns/akn/3.0"><!--default P | TXT -->for:</p>
